commit.message:
Make undo unique per parameter for some filters

This improves all the "favorite" filters to have separate undo
commands for each paramter to give more granularity in undo commands.
These same changes could be made to all other filters to improve
them as well.
Rename filter undo commands and functions

Separate filter undo commands for parameters and keyframes

Start a new undo command for individual paramaters and keyframes
in filters.

This method works for all keyframs in the keyframe panel.

Tracking of individual parameters is only implemented for the color
grading filter.
fix warnings in AudioVectorScopeWidget
add Ambisonic Encoder audio filter
fix update Ambisonic Decoder VUI with keyframes
add a visual indication for Ambisonic Decoder
fix #1524 errors with relative paths as CLI args
fix misleading parameter name

fix Zoom Timeline to Fit sometimes incorrect

https://forum.shotcut.org/t/zoom-timeline-to-fit-does-not-work-
sometimes/43446
missing parenthesis
fix #1523 Qt version in README

Fix filter commands are not created after other commands

Steps to reproduce:
1) Modify a filter on a timeline clip
2) Move the timeline clip
3) Modify the filter again

Since the filter was not reselected, modificatoins for step 3 do not
result in an undo command. This change detects that situation and
creates a new command.

Add configurable time format (#1520)

* Add configurable time format

* Resolve review comments for time format setting

* cleanup Settings > Time Format

---------

Co-authored-by: Dan Dennedy <dan@dennedy.org>
